source.en: Blaser, Magdalena "Myths of the Cofán people"

sentences.text: Tayopi tsai'mbi'o canqquefa tsu pasa fae tsandie Shaningipi qquen inisecho'cho Aguarico na'en otafani canse'cho tise tsa'o'sundeccui'ccu.

values.value: Many years ago, a man named Shaningipi lived at the Aguarico river bank with his family.

sentences.text: Tise tsu an'bian fae onque'nge coenzave.
Tise'ta tsu tsave tisia'caen cansepa coenza pushesuve da.

values.value: She lived for many years with her parents,

sentences.text: Coenzave dapa tsandie've tsa'nduye asi'ttaembe opatsse can'jen.

values.value: and grew old withough even thinking of getting married.

sentences.text: Tsa'caen opatsse ñoe can'jen'cho tsu fae cose ayo'o fae dusunga tsandie me'nde'via'ma.

values.value: But one might she had a dream of a handsome young man.

sentences.text: Tsama ayo'opa tsu mingae'qque asi'ttaembi.

values.value: First, she didn't think much of that dream at all.

sentences.text: Tsa'ma tsa'caen ayo'o ashaemba pui cose toeveyi ayo'je.

values.value: But once dreamt, the dream would come back,

sentences.text: Tsa'caen shacambe ayo'jepa asi'ttaeñe ashaen.

values.value: unfalteringly, every single night. So she started to think:

sentences.text: Tsa'caen ashaemba ñoa'me in'jan tsa tsandie'ma.

values.value: "Perhaps I really want to get married."

sentences.text: Pui cose ayo'o canse tsai'mbi'tssi ccovuve.
Tsa'caen cansepa ñoa'me tsa pushesuja tsa tsandie've in'jañe ashaen.

values.value: and in doing so, she truly fell in love with the man of her dreams.

sentences.text: Ashaemba puini injancco'fa.
Tsandie in'jamba pushesu'qque in'jansi tsandie'ja cose'ninda pushesuni jipa fae'ngae ccuipa ana'jeñe ashaen.

values.value: so they made love at night.

sentences.text: Tsa'caen ashaemba pui cose jipaen.
Tise'ja cose'ninda ande tso'siye jipa atambi'mbinga napipa tse'ttie somboya.
Sombopa vasia've tise injan'je'cho pushesuni mangu jaya.
Tsa'caen japa vasia've asicconga ansundeya.
Ansundepa anamba'cconga fae'ngae cuiya.

Tsa'caen japa vasia've asicconga ansundeya.
Ansundepa anamba'cconga fae'ngae cuiya.
Tsa'cansi pushesumbe antiandeccuja atte'je'fa pui sinte tise ja'je'choma.
Tsa'caen tsa tsandie jipa ja'jesi dusunga pushesuja surie da.
Tsonsi tise antiandeccuja da'ñomba a'fa'fa.
Da'ñomba tisu'pa antiama afa'fa qquen supa:
Iyofa du'shu'an qui isuye queja surie da'je.
Iyofa dushucco'e qui isuye tson'jen.
Qquen tsu da'ño'fa tsa tsandie anambaccu'ye jangipa jayipa atambi'mbinga ne pipa andema jeñamba iyofa'caen ja'jesi.
Tise'ja ande tso'sini canse'chopa tseni ja'je.
Tsa'camba tsene pushesuni ji'je.
Tsa'caen Surie dapa can'jemba tsa pushesuja tsandie du'shuve isu.
Tsa'caen tsandie du'shuve isupa Coancoame inisian.
Tsa du'shuja tise cundyi'je'fama bia'ave an'bian.
Tsa tsu can'jen coen tise mama Vatsirai'ccu.
Coemba shagattu.
Shagattupa can'jen dusungave da.
Coancoanda tsu fae tsandie du'shu.
Tise chuite osha'cho cofeqque'sui'ccu co'fe tsu coen, accui'ccoi'ccu, panza'suve dapa, shavoi'ccu toya'caen faesui'ccu.
Tsa'caen coemba can'je'ni tise antiandeccu sambirive seña'su oshaequini jayi'fa.
Tsa'caen jayi'fasi tise'qque fae'ngae jaye in'jan.
Faequi tayo shagattupa can'jemba tise ton'tomba seña'su oshaiquini seña'su jayi'fasi fae'ngae ja.
Tsa'caen tisepai'ccu fae'ngae sambirive seña'su japa Aguarico oshei'quini napi'fa.
Tise ton'tombaja seña'bama isupa angaji'fa.
Tsonsi attepa tise mama o'vama isupa fae'ngae ja.
Tsa'caen japa oshei'quinga napipa jayipa sambiri sheque'choma atte'fa.
Attepa tsa du'shuja avuja.
Avujapa señañe ashaen'fa.
Tise ton'tombaja seña'bama isupa señañe ashaen'fa tise can ccutsu'ni.
Tsomba pa'cco seña'bama sefaen'fani'qque sambirija pambisi attepa su:
- Ñañinda gi biasembitsse sambirima fi'ttiya.
- ¿Jongoesui'ccu qui tsa'cantsseja tsoña mechota?
- Mecho'a'qque gi fi'ttiye oshaya.
Caña'jen'fa'se.
Qquen supa naenga cca'yapa tise cundyi'je'fama na'enga andian.
Tsa'caen andiamba tise tivei'ccu sintticashipa coenseña coenseña qquen afa.
Tise tsa'caen tson'jen'nijan sambirija paye buttocco'fa.
Tsonsi attepa fundo'je.
¡ Junde japa indi'nga'faja ti'tsse randema!
Tsonsi pañamba asi'ttaen ccutsupa chi'ga'ma re'ri'ccoe tai'nga'fa tise'pa o'vanga.
Tsomba fae'nga fuitepa taipa tsaoni ja'fa.
Japa ccuiñasi tise mamajan cui'ccuma cui'ña nanimba ja.
Japa o'vama isupa tise mamajan avujapa naeni tssaña'su jayi.
Tson'ni tise ton'ton chu'ja su:
Giyatsse qui cashiyate sambiri tssipopoccumajan, tise cundyi'je'fai'ccu tsu sambirimajan fi'ttipa'e i'ya.
Qquen tise ton'ton afa'je'ninda tise quinshi'nge Coancoanjan tse'tti paña'jen.
Tsa'caen pañamba tise ton'toma iyicca'ye.
Tise'ma amunde'fa'o qquen susi.
Tsa'ma tise mamajan otaen nanimba ttu'se.
Ttu'sesi amba iyiccae'sui'ccuyi japa ana.
Anañe japa pa'cco cose asittae'bangayi a'ta ma'caen tise ton'toma tsoña'chove.
Asittaen'jemba shinccapa te'tama du'shuve tsomba qqueñamba tise'ma in'jan omando tise'ma indipa tsangae vanaeñe.
Tsa'caen in'jamba iyiccae'sui'ccuyi a'tapa sinte'yi tise ufacco'ccoma isupa tsampiningae ja.
Japa tise asi'ttaemba in'janqquia'caen shinccapa te'tama isupa oma'ndo du'shuve ñoña.
Tsa'caen ñoñamba fae'ccoma quini'jin chandonga ppiñamba faesumajan tise ufacco'cco tsutopanga dyaiñamba sime tsaoni tsui jiña.
Tsa'caen tsomba jiñasi tise ton'tonjan oma'ndo du'shuma attepa avujapa butto.
Buttopa catsepa su:
- Ñanga afeja.
- Tsonsi su: Faesuta tsu toeni catiye.
Que in'janinda gi tu'i angaya, cuintsu que japa tisutsse ansundepa tisumbetsse isuye.
Qquen supa anamba ccaqui a'ta sinte jangipa ronda'je tise'ma angaye.
Tsa oma'ndo du'shuja faefayi'cco teva'pave an'mbian: cu'a, quiopa, inzia, sin'an, toya'caen totoa'ma.
Tsa'cansi tise ton'tonjan avujapa sinte'yi jangipa cui'ccuma cu'ipa jen'da jinge qquen supa ja'fa.
Biani japa napi'fa.
Ca'tsa napiji'ninda oma'ndo du'shu fundo'je quini'jin changoye.
